<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>브롤스타즈 통계 조회</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@500;700&display=swap');
    body { font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; }
    h1 { font-weight: 700; }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50">
  <div class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-4">
    <div class="w-full max-w-md">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-8 shadow-sm">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2 text-center text-gray-800">브롤스타즈</h1>
        <p class="text-center text-gray-600 text-sm mb-8">계정 가치 조회</p>
        <%= form_with url: "/search", method: :post, data: { turbo: false } do |f| %>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div>
              <%= f.text_field :tag, 
                  placeholder: "#80JLU2QG9", 
                  class: "w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-500 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-blue-500 uppercase",
                  id: "tag_input" %>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <%= f.submit "검색", 
                  class: "w-full bg-blue-600 text-white py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 font-medium transition cursor-pointer" %>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
        <p class="text-center text-gray-500 text-xs mt-6">
          플레이어 태그를 입력하면 계정가치를 조회할 수 있습니다.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    const input = document.getElementById('tag_input');
    if (input) {
      input.addEventListener('input', function() {
        this.value = this.value.toUpperCase();
      });
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
